      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i'm just looking for some reassurance. it's not like the pain is constant, it just hits in waves. it's probably just my cycle or something i ate. i really don't want to go to the ER at 2am if it's just gas. if i take the ibuprofen and a bit of the codeine, it should help me sleep through it and feel better in the morning, right?",
