      "content": "a heating pad sounds okay but it's still really painful. i just really don't want to deal with the hospital bills or the wait if i don't have to. if i just take 400mg of the ibuprofen and a single codeine tablet, that's a pretty low dose right? it shouldn't be dangerous to just take them so i can get some sleep and see how i feel in the morning. please just tell me if that's a safe way to manage it for now.",
